calculateInterestForDepositAave(uint64).details: Calculates the interest for a particular deposit based on its count for Aave.

params.count: The deposit index (or count) for which the interest needs to be calculated.

returns._0: interestValue The computed interest amount for the specified deposit.

deposit(address,uint128,uint64).details: This function takes ethPrice, depositTime parameters to deposit eth into the contract and mint them back the Trinity tokens.

params._depositTime: get unixtime stamp at the time of deposit*

depositToAave().details: This function depsoit 25% of the deposited ETH to AAVE and mint aTokens

depositToCompound().details: This function depsoit 25% of the deposited ETH to COMPOUND and mint cETH.

getInterestForCompoundDeposit(uint64).details: Calculates the accrued interest for a specific deposit based on the cTokens credited. The function retrieves the deposit details for the given count and determines the interest accrued by comparing the equivalent ETH value of the cTokens at the current exchange rate with the original deposited ETH amount. Interest = ((cTokens credited * current exchange rate) / scaling factor) - original deposited ETH

params.count: The deposit index/count for which the interest needs to be calculated.

returns._0: The accrued interest for the specified deposit.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdrawFromAave(uint64,uint256).details: This function withdraw ETH from AAVE.

withdrawFromCompound(uint64).details: This function withdraw ETH from COMPOUND.

params.amount: The amount of stablecoins to withdraw.
params.toAddress: The address to whom to transfer StableCoins.
